---
title: 微搜索 - 最好用的站内搜索工具
keywords: 搜索引擎,站内搜索,应用内搜索,搜索API
description: 最好用的站内搜索工具
nosearch: true
---

.brand
  .wrap
    .row
      .large-12.columns
        %h2.text-center 微搜索
        %p.text-center 最好用的站内搜索引擎
    %br
    %form.row.collapse
      .large-3.columns.medium-2.small-1
        %p
      .large-5.columns.medium-6.small-7
        %input#ts-search-input{type: 'text', placeholder: '例如：自定义样式'}
      .large-1.columns.medium-2.small-2.end
        %input.button.orange{type: 'submit', value: '搜索'}
    .row
      .large-12.columns
        %ul.small-block-grid-3
          %li.text-center
            = image_tag 'brand2.png', alt: 'Autocomplete'
            %p 即时搜索，自动补全
          %li.text-center
            = image_tag 'brand1.png', alt: 'Analytics'
            %p 搜索分析与可视化
          %li.text-center
            = image_tag 'brand3.png', alt: 'Simple Installation'
            %p 快速，稳定，弹性
  %br
.steps
  .step-title.wrap.white-bg
    .row
      .large-12.columns
        %h2 最少只需3步，给你的站点添加微搜索功能
        %br
      %hr
      %br
    .row.show-for-medium-up
      .large-12.columns
        %div{'data-magellan-expedition' => 'fixed'}
          %dl.sub-nav
            .sub-nav-body
              %dd{:'data-magellan-arrival' => 'step1'}
                %a{:href => "#step1"} 1. 创建搜索引擎
              %dd{:'data-magellan-arrival' => 'step2'}
                %a{:href => "#step2"} 2. 添加域名
              %dd{:'data-magellan-arrival' => 'step3'}
                %a{:href => "#step3"} 3. 安装
    .row.show-for-small-only
      %div{'data-magellan-expedition' => 'fixed'}
        %ul.sub-nav
          .sub-nav-body
            %li{:'data-magellan-arrival' => 'step1'}
              %a{:href => "#step1"} 1. 创建搜索引擎
            %li{:'data-magellan-arrival' => 'step2'}
              %a{:href => "#step2"} 2. 添加域名
            %li{:'data-magellan-arrival' => 'step3'}
              %a{:href => "#step3"} 3. 安装
  .step.wrap
    .row
      .large-12.columns
        %a{:name => "step1"}
        %h3{'data-magellan-destination' => 'step1'}
          .label 1
          创建搜索引擎
        = image_tag 'step1.png'
  .step.wrap.white-bg
    .row
      .large-12.columns
        %a{:name => "step2"}
        %h3{'data-magellan-destination' => 'step2'}
          .label 2
          添加域名
        %br
        = image_tag 'step2.png'
  .step.wrap
    .row
      .large-12.columns
        %a{:name => "step3"}
        %h3{'data-magellan-destination' => 'step3'}
          .label 3
          安装
        %br
        = image_tag 'step3.png'
.welcome.wrap.white-bg
  .row
    .large-12.columns.text-center
      %a.button.large{:href => "/plan.html"} 立即试用
.welcome.wrap
  .row
    .large-12.columns
      %ul.small-block-grid-3.large-block-grid-5
        %li
          %a{href: 'http://baozouribao.com/'}
            = image_tag 'logo-baozouribao.png'
        %li
          %a{href: 'http://www.shanbay.com/'}
            = image_tag 'logo-shanbay.png'
        %li
          %a{href: 'http://qng.im/'}
            = image_tag 'logo-qng.png'
        %li
          %a{href: 'http://teahour.fm/'}
            = image_tag 'logo-teahour.jpg'
        %li
          %a{href: 'http://easydatasheet.cn/'}
            = image_tag 'logo-easydatasheet.png'

- content_for :onready do
  :plain
    $('li.nav-home').addClass('active');
